      • isValid

        public void isValid()
             throws iramat.dosiseed.model.Incoherence
        Check if the model is valid for the generation of PTF file. The method is also triggered when the tab changing, to prevent eventual null pointer or other runtime exception.
        Throws:
        iramat.dosiseed.model.Incoherence - the exception when the model is inconsistent.
